{
  "texts": [
    "We use the Llama 4 Maverick model as the base policy and an internal RLHF infrastructure to conduct the RL training.",
    "The training prompts are manually written by the vendor Surge and the rubrics are synthetically generated by the rubric generator introduced in Section 4.2.",
    "For the rubric verifier, we also finetune a Llama 4 Maverick model following the recipe mentioned in Section 4.3.",
    "Evaluation.",
    "We evaluate the performance of RIFL and the baseline on three challenging IF benchmarks, including our proposed AdvancedIF benchmark (Section 3.1) and two public benchmarks: IFEval (Zhou et al., 2023) and MultiChallenge (Deshpande et al., 2025) to test both in-distribution and out-of-distribution generalization."
  ]
}